-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack wxWidgets2.8-2.8.11.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./wxWidgets2.8-2.8.11.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libwx_baseu2.8-devel-2.8.11.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libwx_baseu2.8_0-2.8.11.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libwx_gtk2u2.8-devel-2.8.11.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libwx_gtk2u2.8_0-2.8.11.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/python-wx2.8-2.8.11.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/wxWidgets2.8-2.8.11.0-X-src.tar.bz2

A list of files in each package can be found by running:
cygcheck -l PACKAGE [PACKAGE2 ...]

-------------------------------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 2.8.11.0-1 -----
Version bump.
Added iODBC support.

----- version 2.8.10.1-2 -----
Rebuilt to use auto-import instead of dllimport; may require rebuild
of some dependent packages.
Dropped dependencies on obsolete libesd and libgnomeprint.
Added patches for CVE-2009-2369 and for compatibility with glib-2.22.

----- version 2.8.10.1-1 -----
Version bump.
Editra is now available as its own package.

----- version 2.8.9.2-10 -----
Initial release of 2.8 branch for Cygwin 1.7.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://sourceware.org/cygwinports/
